overview.en: ETD is an encrypted digital currency based on the ERC20 underlying protocol jointly developed by Venezuela and China blockchain experts. Its goal is to build a secure smart asset chain and apply blockchain technology and digital currency to business and trade.
overview.zh: ETD是由委内瑞拉和中国区块链专家共同开发的一种基于ERC20底层协议的加密数字货币。它的目标是建立一个安全的智能资产链，并将区块链技术和数字货币应用于商业和贸易。
